=== 截角小星形十二面體 ===
{{main|截角小星形十二面體}}
[[File:Small_stellated_dodecahedron_truncations.gif|thumb]]
截去所有頂點的小星形十二面體{{#tag:ref|產生半正多面體所用的截角，即確保截角完後的面皆要等邊的截角。{{#tag:ref|Coxeter, H.S.M. Chapter 8: Truncation, ''Regular Polytopes'',<ref name="Coxeter Regular Polytopes 1973">[[哈羅德·斯科特·麥克唐納·考克斯特|Coxeter, H.S.M.]]; Regular Polytopes (third edition). Dover Publications Inc. {{isbn|0-486-61480-8}}</ref> pp. 145–154}}<ref>Norman Johnson, ''Uniform Polytopes'', Manuscript (1991)</ref>|group="註"|name="Truncation (geometry)"}}<ref name="GlossaryForHyperspace Truncation">{{GlossaryForHyperspace | anchor=Truncation | title=Truncation }}</ref>可構成一個外觀與[[正十二面體|正十二面體]]無異的退化[[均勻多面體|均勻多面體]]。<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.mathconsult.ch/static/unipoly/background.html | title = Background Information of Uniform polyhedra | author = mathconsult | access-date = 2021-08-20 | archive-date = 2020-02-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200224045109/http://www.mathconsult.ch/static/unipoly/background.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="article maeder1993uniform">{{Cite journal
  |title=Uniform polyhedra
  |author=Maeder, Roman E
  |journal=The Mathematica Journal
  |volume=3
  |number=4
  |pages=48--57
  |year=1993
  |publisher=Citeseer
  |url=http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/download?doi=10.1.1.52.2157&rep=rep1&type=pdf
  |access-date=2021-08-20
  |archive-date=2021-08-23
  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210823170157/http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/messages/downloadsexceeded.html
  |dead-url=no
  }}</ref>這種多面體在考克斯特記號中可以用{{CDD|node|5|node_1|5|rat|d2|node_1}}表示。<ref>[[Harold_Scott_MacDonald_Coxeter|Coxeter]], ''The Evolution of Coxeter-Dynkin diagrams'', [Nieuw Archief voor Wiskunde 9 (1991) 233-248]</ref>雖然其外觀與正十二面體無異，然而這種立體並非十二面體，而是一種退化的二十四面體，其由24個面、90條邊和60個頂點組成，其中24個面為12個正五邊形和12個繞兩圈的正五邊形組成，整體可以視為是每個頂點都是2個十邊形和1個五邊形之公共頂點的抽象等角二十四面體的具像化。<ref name="article grunbaum2007graphs">{{Cite journal
  |title=Graphs of polyhedra; polyhedra as graphs
  |author=Grünbaum, Branko
  |journal=Discrete Mathematics
  |volume=307
  |number=3-5
  |pages=445--463
  |year=2007
  |publisher=Elsevier
  |doi=10.1016/j.disc.2005.09.037}}</ref>

不同的截角深度也會產生不同的幾何體：
