=== 北炯立體 ===
{{see also|星形四角化菱形十二面體#北炯立體}}
[[哲養·北炯|哲養·北炯]]曾在其論文中探討星形十二面體，<ref name="article beziau2003new">{{Cite journal
  |title=New light on the square of oppositions and its nameless corner
  |author=Béziau, Jean-Yves
  |journal=Logical Investigations
  |volume=10
  |number=2003
  |pages=218--232
  |year=2003}}</ref>但不慎將以五邊形組成的[[正十二面體|正十二面體]]之星形化體與菱形組成的[[菱形十二面體|菱形十二面體]]之星形化體搞混了。後來莫雷帝將其描述為在正十二面體的面上加入[[五角錐|五角錐]]組成的立體，<ref name="article moretti2010critics">{{Cite journal
  |title=The critics of paraconsistency and of many-valuedness and the geometry of oppositions
  |author=Moretti, Alessio
  |journal=Logic and Logical Philosophy
  |volume=19
  |number=1-2
  |pages=63--94
  |year=2010}}</ref>即小星形十二面體。
後來，漢士·史梅斯特（Hans Smessaert）等人才以[[星形四角化菱形十二面體|星形四角化菱形十二面體]]的結構完成北炯最初探討的議題。<ref name="incollection smessaert2015beziau">{{Citation
  |title=Béziau’s contributions to the logical geometry of modalities and quantifiers
  |author=Smessaert, Hans and Demey, Lorenz
  |periodical=The road to universal logic
  |pages=475--493
  |year=2015
  |publisher=Springer}}</ref>
{| class=wikitable
|- valign=top
|[[File:Dodekaederstern.png|180px]]<br/>莫雷帝描述的北炯立體<br/>（實為小星形十二面體）
|[[File:Escher's_Solid_Rhombic_Dodecahedron_Stellation.svg|180px]]<br/>漢士·史梅斯特描述的北炯立體
|}
=== 星形鑲嵌圖 ===
其也可以視為一系列施萊夫利符號中可利用{n/2,n}表示的星形鑲嵌之一，例如[[七階七角星鑲嵌|七階七角星鑲嵌]]：<ref>[[John_Horton_Conway|John H. Conway]], Heidi Burgiel, Chaim Goodman-Strass, ''The Symmetries of Things'' 2008, {{isbn|978-1-56881-220-5}} (Chapter 19, The Hyperbolic Archimedean Tessellations)</ref><ref>{{Cite book|title=The Beauty of Geometry: Twelve Essays|url=https://archive.org/details/beautyofgeometry0000coxe|year=1999|publisher=Dover Publications|lccn=99035678|isbn=0-486-40919-8|chapter=Chapter 10: Regular honeycombs in hyperbolic space}}</ref>
{{星形多面體和鑲嵌系列}}

=== 對偶複合體 ===
{{main|{{link-en|複合大十二面體小星形十二面體|Compound_of_small_stellated_dodecahedron_and_great_dodecahedron}}}}
:[[File:Compound_of_great_dodecahedron_and_small_stellated_dodecahedron.png|200px]]
小星形十二面體與其對偶多面體的複合體為'''複合小星形十二面體大十二面體'''。其共有24個面、60條邊和24個頂點，其[[歐拉特徵數|尤拉示性數]]為-12，虧格為7，<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://bulatov.org/polyhedra/uniform_compounds/uc40.html|title=compound of great dodecahedron and small stellated dodecahedron|publisher=bulatov.org|access-date=2021-08-21|archive-date=2021-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305162653/http://bulatov.org/polyhedra/uniform_compounds/uc40.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>而在這個立體圖形中，僅有小星形十二面體可見，大十二面體完全隱沒於小星形十二面體而不可見。<ref>{{MathWorld |title=Great Dodecahedron-Small Stellated Dodecahedron Compound |urlname=GreatDodecahedron-SmallStellatedDodecahedronCompound}}</ref>

